## Interface com Outros Squads

### Quem depende de nos

| Squad | O que consome |
|---|---|
| Squad Orders | FK clientId nos pedidos |
| Squad Financial | FK clientId em AR |
| Squad Sync PF | upsertByProFinancasId() |
| Squad Search | Evento client.created/updated para indexacao |

### De quem dependemos

| Squad | O que consumimos |
|---|---|
| Squad Reference Data | ClientClassification, DeliveryRoute, PaymentMethod |
| Squad Infra | PrismaService |
| Squad Auth | Guards, @Roles |

